Name: SNOMED_CT
Title: SNOMED CT (all versions)
Descriptino: SNOMED CT is the most comprehensive and precise clinical health terminology product in the world, owned and distributed around the world by The International Health Terminology Standards Development Organisation (IHTSDO).

Name: TitleType
Title: TitleType
Descriptino: Used to express the reason and specific aspect for the variant title, such as language and specific language.

Name: RoleCode
Title: RoleCode
Descriptino: A set of codes further specifying the kind of Role; specific classification codes for further qualifying RoleClass codes.

Name: ResearchDataAccessCode
Title: Research Data Access Codes
Descriptino: Enumerated list of access codes such as dbGaP consent codes among others.

Name: ResearchDataAccessType
Title: Research Data Access Type Codes
Descriptino: Enumerated list of access type codes such as 'Open Access', 'Registered Access' and 'Controlled Access'
